  number: 8,
  title: "Building Your Magic System",
  intro: [Magic is often what makes a fantasy world feel like fantasy, but if magic can do everything then magic really means nothing. Constraints, rules, costs and limits on the magic system is what makes the magic system memorable. When your character reaches for their power, we need to know what they're risking, what they're capable of, and what's completely beyond them.],
