  headers: ("Type", "How It Works", "Romantic Potential", "Example"),
  rows: (
    ([Elemental], [Control over natural forces (fire, water, earth, air)], [Complementary or opposing elements between leads; loss of control reflecting emotional state], [#emph[Avatar], #emph[The Priory of the Orange Tree]]),
    ([Spellcasting], [Words, gestures, or rituals produce specific effects], [Shared rituals as intimacy; spells gone wrong creating vulnerability], [#emph[Harry Potter], #emph[The Name of the Wind]]),
    ([Innate/Inborn], [Powers you're born with, often tied to bloodline], [Bloodline politics affecting who can love whom; awakening powers tied to emotional growth], [#emph[X-Men], #emph[Graceling], #emph[Ninth House]]),
    ([Blood/Sacrifice], [Power drawn from blood, pain, or giving something up], [Sacrificing for each other; shared pain as connection], [#emph[Blood and Ash], #emph[Daughter of No Worlds]]),
    ([Emotional/Will-Based], [Magic fuelled by feelings, desire, or force of will], [Falling in love makes magic stronger or more dangerous; emotions as vulnerability], [#emph[The Rage of Dragons]]),
    ([Bond-Based], [Magic tied to a connection with another being], [The bond itself becomes the romantic vehicle; forced proximity through magical partnership], [#emph[Fourth Wing], #emph[His Dark Materials]]),
    ([Artifact-Based], [Power resides in objects, not people], [Shared custody of powerful objects; gifting enchanted items as intimacy], [#emph[Lord of the Rings]]),
    ([Transformation], [Ability to change form], [True form as vulnerability; accepting someone's other shape as acceptance of their whole self], [#emph[ACOTAR] (shifting)]),
    ([Necromancy], [Power over death, spirits, or life's boundary], [Stigma and secrecy; raising stakes around mortality; "I'd bring you back" as ultimate declaration], [#emph[Gideon the Ninth], #emph[Sabriel]]),
    ([Bargain/Contract], [Power gained through deals or binding agreements], [Bargains that force proximity or create obligation; loopholes as plot devices], [#emph[ACOTAR] (bargains)]),
    ([Symbiotic/Parasitic], [Magic requires or is enhanced by another being], [Dependency as vulnerability; needing someone as both power source and person], [#emph[Venom], #emph[The Fifth Season]]),
    ([Music/Art-Based], [Creation through song, art, or expression], [Creating something together; art as emotional revelation; songs that only mean something to two people], [#emph[Wintersong]]),
    ([True Names], [Power from knowing the true nature of things], [Knowing someone's true name as ultimate intimacy and ultimate weapon], [#emph[Earthsea], #emph[The Name of the Wind]]),
    ([Psychic/Mental], [Mind-reading, telekinesis, mental influence], [Thoughts you can't hide; mental shields as emotional walls; choosing to let someone in], [#emph[Shatter Me], #emph[Carrie]]),
